main event: Two objects were observed in Wheaton, Maryland, moving erratically at high speeds and making abrupt turns for a duration of 12 minutes on May 31, 1964.
interesting points: The objects came from the southeast and moved towards the northwest., The sighting lasted for 12 minutes from 2155Z to 2207Z., The motion of the objects included changing directions and heights., No sound was reported during the observation., This event is part of a larger collection of UFO sightings recorded in the Project Blue Book.
sighted object: two unidentified flying objects exhibiting erratic motion
witness description: A woman and her husband along with their three children witnessed the objects.
